videos.description: NIU's Shawun Lurry picks off Tanner Lee and returns it 87 yards to give the Huskies the 7-0 lead over Nebraska.
videos.headline: NIU's Lurry returns Nebraska's pass 87 yards for the TD

videos.description: Nebraska QB Tanner Lee is hit and NIU's Jawuan Johnson intercepts the pass and returns it 25 yards for a Huskies TD.
videos.headline: Jawuan Johnson gets NIU's second pick-six against Nebraska

videos.description: NIU's Jalen Embry muffs the Nebraska punt and it is recovered by Nebraska's Marquel Dismuke
videos.headline: Nebraska catches a break with an NIU muffed punt

videos.description: Nebraska QB Tanner Lee scores on a 4 yard TD run after the NIU muffed punt to cut its deficit to 14-7
videos.headline: Nebraska gets on the board with a 4 yard TD

videos.description: Nebraska's Tanner Lee connects with JD Spielman for 36 yards all the way to the 2 yard line.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Spielman catches the 36-yard pass deep into NIU territory

videos.description: Nebrska QB Tanner Lee fights to cross the goal line and give the Cornhuskers their first lead over NIU.
videos.headline: Nebraska takes their first lead of the game

videos.description: NIU QB Daniel Santacaterina throws a pass to Christian Blake for 47 yds for a 1st down
videos.headline: NIU's Blake quiets the Nebraska crowd

videos.description: NIU's Jordan Huff runs through Nebraska tacklers to regain the lead for NIU
videos.headline: NIU responds with a quick TD
